- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is a possible category as the course introduces students to computer software and problem-solving skills. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is another possible category as the course is grounded in classical logic. 
- cs.DB (Databases) is a less likely category, but the paper mentions the course expanding into areas such as massive databases.
